sequenceDiagram
  participant User as 用户
  participant GW as Duplex Gateway
  participant Agent as 本地 Agent
  participant TTS as 本地 TTS

  User->>GW: 帮我总结这份合同
  GW-->>GW: silence >= threshold
  GW->>Agent: commit_turn("帮我总结这份合同")
  Agent->>TTS: 开始回复
  TTS-->>User: 我先帮你看一下合同...
  User->>GW: 等一下，先重点看付款周期
  GW->>TTS: interrupt_tts
  GW->>Agent: commit_turn("先重点看付款周期")
  Agent->>TTS: 生成新的回复
  TTS-->>User: 好的，我优先看付款周期
